summary: A Dunmer woman who obviously isn't choosing wisely. Word has it that she can be found at Haelgas bunkhouse in Riften. Try not to wake her. UNPetite Standalone Body.
descriptionHtml:
Torasa is a Dunmer mercenary/woman for hire, who is apparently making bad decisions. She'll follow just about anyone who will show her the slightest bit of attention. She can be found, most likely passed out, at Haelga's bunkhouse in Riften.

Fun Facts:
Level 4-80
Essential
Marriage?
2 Handed weapons
Any Crime
Doesn't smile
